OL,3,CMPs call for local authorities to be
OL,4,Chanded control of council tax
OL,6,FCouncils should be given control over
OL,7,Fcouncil tax as the current broken link
OL,8,Fbetween the local charge and the
OL,9,Fquality of services risks undermining
OL,10,Flocal democracy, MPs have warned.
OL,12,FAn inquiry into the financial
OL,13,Fsustainability of local government
OL,14,Fconcluded that councils should be
OL,15,Fgiven interim powers ahead of reform
OL,16,Fof "the most unfair and regressive tax
OL,17,Fin use in England today", which it
OL,18,Fsaid should be more of a priority for
OL,19,Fthe Government.
