OL,3,CMPs call for local authorities to be
OL,4,Chanded control of council tax
OL,6,FThis would include giving individual
OL,7,Fauthorities the power to revalue
OL,8,Fproperties in their area, define
OL,9,Fproperty bands, set the rates for
OL,10,Fthose bands, and apply discounts, the
OL,11,FCommons Housing, Communities and Local
OL,12,FGovernment Committee said.
OL,14,FThe report said a broader devolution
OL,15,Fof fiscal powers, such as applying
OL,16,Ftourist tax, should also form part of
OL,17,Ffixing local government finances,
OL,18,Fwhich have been under growing strain
OL,19,Fsince the onset of austerity in the
OL,20,F2010s led to reduced funding.
