OL,3,CMPs call for local authorities to be
OL,4,Chanded control of council tax
OL,6,FDeputy Prime Minister Angela Rayner
OL,7,Frecently said she wanted "more push"
OL,8,Ftowards fiscal devolution as part of
OL,9,Fthe Government's pledge to transfer
OL,10,Fcentral decision making to local areas.
OL,12,FThe committee also recommended that
OL,13,Fcentral government ringfencing of
OL,14,Ffunding be replaced with "a rigorous
OL,15,Foutcomes-based system of
OL,16,Faccountability", so that local
OL,17,Fauthorities are held accountable for
OL,18,Fachieving against a set of agreed
OL,19,Foutcomes within their overall budgets,
OL,20,Fnot for meeting spending targets.
