OL,6,FCouncil tax bill rises hit 5% in April
OL,7,Ffor the third year in a row, as almost
OL,8,Fall councils increased bills up to, or
OL,9,Fclose to, the maximum permitted.
OL,11,FThe revaluation of properties has long
OL,12,Fbeen called for, with council tax
OL,13,Fbands in England still based on
OL,14,Fproperty values in 1991.
