OL,3,CMPs call for local authorities to be
OL,4,Chanded control of council tax
OL,6,FThe Institute for Fiscal Studies found
OL,7,Fthat the most expensive properties
OL,8,F(Band H) attract three times as much
OL,9,Ftax as the least valuable (Band A)
OL,10,Fdespite being worth more than eight
OL,11,Ftimes more now, as prices have risen
OL,12,Fmost in affluent areas.
OL,14,F"Council tax is therefore both
OL,15,Fincreasingly out of date and
OL,16,Farbitrary, and highly regressive with
OL,17,Frespect to property values," it added.
