OL,3,CMPs call for local authorities to be
OL,4,Chanded control of council tax
OL,6,FA recent analysis commissioned by the
OL,7,FCounty Councils Network found allowing
OL,8,Fcouncils to administer and retain
OL,9,Ftaxes generated locally would boost
OL,10,Ffunding for services by more than #4
OL,11,Fbillion in many areas and
OL,12,F"supercharge" economic growth.
OL,14,FFlorence Eshalomi, Labour chair of the
OL,15,Fcommittee said: "When residents are
OL,16,Fpaying more and more in taxes but
OL,17,Fseeing less and less in regular,
OL,18,Feveryday services, such as libraries
OL,19,Fand fixing potholes, then trust in
OL,20,Flocal democracy is at risk of being
OL,21,Fundermined.
