OL,3,CMPs call for local authorities to be
OL,4,Chanded control of council tax
OL,6,F"If, as a country, we are going to
OL,7,Fdeliver growth and improve local
OL,8,Fservices, Westminster needs to ease
OL,9,Fits grip and let councils have more
OL,10,Fpower to control their own affairs and
OL,11,Fbe accountable to their own
OL,12,Felectorates."
OL,14,FThe report also called called for the
OL,15,FGovernment to reconsider its decision
OL,16,Fto freeze local housing allowance
OL,17,Frates and extend its support for local
OL,18,Fauthorities to acquire new housing
OL,19,Fstock through the local authority
OL,20,Fhousing fund.
